<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Calendrier de {{ child.firstName }} — Grooty</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --cream: #FAF7F2; --warm: #F2EDE4; --sand: #E8DFD0;
            --forest: #3D5A47; --forest-light: #5A7D68;
            --terracotta: #C4714A;
            --ink: #1C1C1A; --muted: #8A8578;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #B8D4E8 0%, #D6EAF8 40%, #EAF4F8 70%, #E8F5E0 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        /* ── HEADER ── */
        .share-header {
            background: var(--forest);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .share-brand {
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: white;
        }
        .share-brand em { color: #FAD7A0; font-style: italic; }
        .share-child {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .6rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: .85rem;
        }

        /* ── CONTENU ── */
        .main { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem; }

        .week-block {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.9);
            padding: 1.2rem 1.2rem .5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44,62,80,.1);
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .week-label {
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* ── TRAIN ── */
        .train-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 0;
            padding-bottom: .8rem;
            min-width: max-content;
        }

        /* Locomotive */
        .loco { flex-shrink:0; width:80px; margin-right:3px; }
        .loco-body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,#2C3E50,#3D5166);
            border-radius: 14px 6px 6px 14px;
            min-height: 80px;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: white; position: relative; padding: .5rem .3rem;
            box-shadow: 4px 0 12px rgba(44,62,80,.25);
        }
        .loco-chimney {
            position:absolute; top:-14px; left:14px;
            width:12px; height:18px;
            background:#2C3E50; border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;
        }
        .loco-chimney::before {
            content:''; position:absolute; top:-5px; left:-4px;
            width:20px; height:8px;
            background:#3D5166; border-radius:4px;
        }
        .loco-avatar {
            width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;
            border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);margin-bottom:4px;
        }
        .loco-window {
            width:22px;height:14px;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#87CEEB,#B0E0FF);
            border-radius:3px;margin-bottom:5px;
            border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
        }
        .loco-name {
            font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:.58rem;
            font-style:italic;text-align:center;line-height:1.3;
            text-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
        }
        .loco-wheels { display:flex;gap:7px;justify-content:center;padding:4px 0 0; }
        .loco-wheel {
            width:13px;height:13px;border-radius:50%;
            background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%,#666,#111);
            border:2px solid #888;
        }

        .coupler {
            flex-shrink:0;align-self:flex-end;margin-bottom:1.2rem;
            display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1px;
        }
        .coupler-bar { width:8px;height:3px;background:#aaa;border-radius:2px; }
        .coupler-pin { width:3px;height:5px;background:#888;border-radius:1px; }

        /* Wagon */
        .wagon { flex-shrink:0; width:104px; }
        .wagon-body {
            border-radius:10px 10px 4px 4px;
            padding:.5rem .5rem .45rem;
            display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;
            position:relative;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.08), 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        }
        .wagon:nth-child(2n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#D4E6F1,#AED6F1); }
        .wagon:nth-child(3n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#D5F5E3,#A9DFBF); }
        .wagon:nth-child(4n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#FDEBD0,#FAD7A0); }
        .wagon:nth-child(5n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#F9EBEA,#F1948A); }
        .wagon:nth-child(6n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#EAF2FF,#C5D8FA); }
        .wagon:nth-child(7n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#FEF9E7,#F7DC6F); }
        .wagon:nth-child(8n)  .wagon-body { background:linear-gradient(160deg,#F3E5F5,#CE93D8); }
        .wagon.today .wagon-body {
            background:linear-gradient(160deg,#FFF3CD,#FFD700) !important;
        }
        .wagon-window {
            position:absolute;top:6px;right:6px;
            width:14px;height:10px;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#87CEEB,#B0E0FF);
            border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;opacity:.7;
        }
        .wagon-day {
            font-size:.54rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;
            letter-spacing:.07em;color:rgba(0,0,0,.45);
        }
        .wagon-date {
            font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1rem;
            font-weight:700;color:rgba(0,0,0,.65);line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;
        }
        .wagon.today .wagon-date { color:#2C3E50; }
        .ev-block {
            background:rgba(255,255,255,.7);border-radius:7px;
            padding:.28rem .38rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);
        }
        .ev-label {
            font-size:.52rem;line-height:1.35;color:rgba(0,0,0,.65);
            display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px;
        }
        .ev-photo { margin-top:3px;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden; }
        .ev-photo img { width:100%;height:auto;display:block;max-height:80px;object-fit:contain; }
        .wagon-empty .wagon-body {
            background:rgba(255,255,255,.25) !important;
            box-shadow:none;border:1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        }
        .w-wheels { display:flex;gap:7px;justify-content:center;padding:3px 8px 0; }
        .w-wheel {
            width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;
            background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%,#666,#111);
            border:2px solid #888;
        }

        /* ── CTA BAS DE PAGE ── */
        .share-cta {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 2px solid var(--sand);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .share-cta h2 {
            font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: .5rem;
        }
        .share-cta p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: .88rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
            padding: .65rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none; border: none;
        }
        .btn-primary { background: var(--forest); color: white; }
        .btn-ghost {
            background: white; color: var(--muted);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--sand);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

{# Header #}
<div class="share-header">
    <div class="share-brand">Gr<em>oo</em>ty</div>
    <div class="share-child">
        {% if child.avatarPath %}
        <img src="/uploads/events/{{ child.avatarPath }}"
             style="width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'">
        {% endif %}
        Calendrier de <strong>{{ child.firstName }}</strong>
    </div>
    <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}"
       style="padding:.4rem .9rem;border-radius:100px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);
              color:white;text-decoration:none;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:500;
              border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);">
        Créer mon compte
    </a>
</div>

<div class="main">

    {# Bandeau lecture seule #}
    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.6);border-radius:12px;padding:.7rem 1rem;
                margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;
                font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);">
        <span>👁️</span>
        <span>Vous consultez le calendrier de <strong>{{ child.firstName }}</strong> en lecture seule — 2 semaines.</span>
    </div>

    {% set joursFR = {'Mon':'Lun','Tue':'Mar','Wed':'Mer','Thu':'Jeu','Fri':'Ven','Sat':'Sam','Sun':'Dim'} %}
    {% set today   = 'now'|date('Y-m-d') %}

    {% for weekOffset in 0..1 %}
        {% set wStart = 'monday this week'|date_modify('+' ~ weekOffset ~ ' weeks') %}
        {% set wEnd   = wStart|date_modify('+6 days') %}

        <div class="week-block">
            <div class="week-label">
                Semaine {{ wStart|date('W') }} · du {{ wStart|date('d') }} au {{ wEnd|date('d') }} {{ wEnd|date('F Y') }}
            </div>

            <div class="train-row">

                {# Locomotive #}
                <div class="loco">
                    <div class="loco-body">
                        <div class="loco-chimney"></div>
                        {% if child.avatarPath %}
                        <img src="/uploads/events/{{ child.avatarPath }}" class="loco-avatar"
                             onerror="this.outerHTML='<div class=loco-window></div>'">
                        {% else %}
                        <div class="loco-window"></div>
                        {% endif %}
                        <div class="loco-name">{{ child.firstName }}<br>S{{ wStart|date('W') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="loco-wheels">
                        <div class="loco-wheel"></div><div class="loco-wheel"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {% for d in 0..6 %}
                    {% set day     = wStart|date_modify('+' ~ d ~ ' days') %}
                    {% set dayKey  = day|date('Y-m-d') %}
                    {% set isToday = dayKey == today %}
                    {% set dayEvts = weekByDay[weekOffset] is defined and weekByDay[weekOffset][dayKey] is defined
                                     ? weekByDay[weekOffset][dayKey] : [] %}

                    <div class="coupler">
                        <div class="coupler-bar"></div><div class="coupler-pin"></div><div class="coupler-bar"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="wagon {% if isToday %}today{% endif %} {% if dayEvts is empty %}wagon-empty{% endif %}">
                        <div class="wagon-body">
                            <div class="wagon-window"></div>
                            <div class="wagon-day">{{ joursFR[day|date('D')]|default(day|date('D')) }}{% if isToday %} ✦{% endif %}</div>
                            <div class="wagon-date">{{ day|date('d') }}</div>
                            {% for e in dayEvts %}
                            <div class="ev-block">
                                <div class="ev-label">
                                    <span>{% if e.type=='garde' %}🏠{% elseif e.type=='activite' %}🏃{% elseif e.type=='medical' %}🏥{% elseif e.type=='vacances' %}🌴{% else %}📌{% endif %}</span>
                                    <span>{{ e.title|slice(0,16) }}{% if e.title|length > 16 %}…{% endif %}</span>
                                </div>
                                {% if e.image %}
                                <div class="ev-photo">
                                    <img src="/uploads/events/{{ e.image.filePath }}"
                                         onerror="this.parentElement.style.display='none'">
                                </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-wheels"><div class="w-wheel"></div><div class="w-wheel"></div></div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

            </div>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}

    {# CTA bas de page #}
    <div class="share-cta">
        <h2>Vous faites partie de la famille de <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--terracotta)">{{ child.firstName }}</em> ?</h2>
        <p>Créez un compte gratuit pour ajouter des événements, écrire des notes<br>et recevoir les mises à jour en temps réel.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:.8rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn btn-primary">🌿 Créer mon compte</a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn btn-ghost">Se connecter</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;font-size:.75rem;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);">
        Gr<em style="font-style:italic;">oo</em>ty · Agenda familial partagé
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
